Class User

java.lang.Object
org.example.domain.Entity<Long>
org.example.domain.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Observer
Direct Known Subclasses:
Duck, Person
public abstract class User extends Entity<Long> implements Observer
Represents a generic user in the social network. Each user has a unique identifier, a username, an email, and a password.
